misc.synopsis: Udit Shandilya, Daler Mehndi Records'  talented song writer , singer is out with a lovely new song "Titliyan". After the super hit Gudiya Rani, Gadbadi, Sohni Mainu Lagdi, Shukr Hai, Meri Ma, this is Udit's 6th song dedicated to women and this time he has collaborated with another young empowered woman apart from being supported by a label run by a woman. Titliyan is a fun song along with a very encouraging and motivating message which tells us to "respect girls and moreover wants every girl to have faith in themselves and to believe that they are beautiful inside and out and sky is the only limit."
misc.description: Udit Shandilya, Daler Mehndi Records'  talented song writer , singer is out with a lovely new song "Titliyan". After the super hit Gudiya Rani, Gadbadi, Sohni Mainu Lagdi, Shukr Hai, Meri Ma, this is Udit's 6th song dedicated to women and this time he has collaborated with another young empowered woman apart from being supported by a label run by a woman. Titliyan is a fun song along with a very encouraging and motivating message which tells us to "respect girls and moreover wants every girl to have faith in themselves and to believe that they are beautiful inside and out and sky is the only limit."  Apart from being dedicated to women, Titliyan's video is conceived, shot, animated visualised by this young girl from Jammu - You Tuber Sonia Mannotra who has a mind of her own, is extremely talented and  has immense fan following on you tube. 'At DMRecords, we've always supported youth who have the zeal to forge ahead. Collaborating with Sonia has added another streak of joy to out catalogue. I'm a  hard core feminist and it gives me immense pleasure to work on projects that project women in all their glory instead of objectifying them,' says Taran Mehndi.
